      <title>花旗银行驳回纽约欺诈骗局诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/citi-pushes-back-new-york-lawsuit-over-fraud-scams-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-10-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团发言人周二对路透社表示，花旗集团律师已敦促美国地区法官保罗·奥特肯 (Paul Oetken) 驳回美国司法部长莱蒂蒂亚·詹姆斯 (Letitia James) 一月份提起的诉讼，该诉讼指控花旗银行未能向遭受网络诈骗的客户进行赔偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/citi-pushes-back-new-york-lawsuit-over-fraud-scams-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-10-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 21:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
